snippet.description:
The Thug Kitchen cookbook was released last year amidst some controversy. In this review, I do address the issues (albeit lightly) as I don't feel it would be fair to do a review without acknowledging the concerns of cultural misappropriation and racial sensitivity.
To learn more, check out:
Vegan Sistah: http://sistahvegan.com/2014/11/04/video-on-ferguson-thug-kitchen-trayvon-martin-intersections-of-post-race-consciousness-food-justice-and-hip-hop-veganism/

CBC news coverage: http://www.cbc.ca/newsblogs/yourcommunity/2014/09/thug-kitchen-creators-revealed-as-white-race-debate-ensues.html

********************************************************

The recipes tested in this video include Cornmeal Waffles and Strawberry Syrup, Spiced Chickpea Wraps with Tahini Dressing and Vegetable Pad Thai. I also tried the Tofu Scramble Tacos and Cauliflower bites previously but did not film those.

I know a lot of you have and LOVE this book. Remember these cookbook reviews are only only my opinion (and I mention other's opinions if they shared in the food) and it is 100% ok to have a different opinion. We all have different palates depending on what kinds of foods we have been exposed to and what we grew up with.

Buy Thug Kitchen: Eat Like You Give A on Amazon: http://amzn.to/2228o0I

COOKBOOK REVIEW REQUESTS
Here's a link to all the vegan cookbooks that I have access to: https://www.pinterest.com/marystestktchn/vegan-cookbooks-i-have/ Feel free to request reviews for these or others. :-)

Rather read a review? Find my blog post here: http://www.marystestkitchen.com/thug-kitchen-eat-like-you-give-a-cookbook-review/

********************************************************
Other links mentioned in this video:

Baked Spicy Peanut Tofu: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySMpOrEh78w&index=19&list=PL6QDlGTnYxpFjPdhy6SPk3i2fKq_tvHLz

snippet.description: This car is currently for sale by the third owner from new, and he is asking $2500 or best offer for the car.  The car has 84,000 actual miles, but is virtually rust free, and you would NOT believe how clean and well preserved the car is underneath and across the chassis.  The car runs excellent, and the factory cruise control still works nicely, as well as the original Am/Fm radio with the factory speaker in the front and back that are not blown, but still work decently.  Overall, this is a very well-kept example of this particular model coupe.  You do not see these coupes is THIS kind of condition anymore, especially with the number of factory power options that this car has.

snippet.description:
Episode 1 of Cooking with Ginger & Spice! In this episode, Ron & Son whip up a Grilled Chicken sandwich with Asian Pear & Bibimbap Mayonnaise for a cooking contest based on the "Kimchi Chronicles" -- a PBS series (and cookbook) by Marja Vongerichten exploring Korean culture and cooking.

We hope you enjoy episode 1 of our new cooking series! We'll explore Korean cuisine (Son's background), American faves (Ron's background), fusion dishes, and other cuisines from around the world. 

We've talked about starting this up for a while, and it took this contest to kick us into gear! Thanks Marja!

(For bloopers and outtakes from this video, check out http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h8JZyc36Wak)

Spiaggia di Marina di Campo - Comune di Campo nell'Elba - A seguito della trasmissione da parte della TV nazionale di un pregevole servizio apparso ad alcuni malpensanti come una promozione elettorale (a carico del contribuente-abbonato ed a favore di un "casualmente" intervistato candidato). 
Tenuto conto che la medesima trasmissione ha costuito una certa promozione dell'immagine turistica paesana, rappresentando i chilometri di arenile campese con inquadrature opportunamente strette su un mucchio di fango da dragaggio ed inserendo visioni di chiari innocui rivoli in lontananza laddove si parlava di percolati di discarica (merdosetti anzichennò).

Pur ringraziando mamma RAI e chi la ispirò per il "servizietto" fattoci ci corre l'obbligo di precisare quanto segue:

CLIP DESCRIPTION:
Josh (Breckin Meyer) discovers that Rubin (Paulo Costanzo) has accidentally mailed a sex tape he made to his long-distance girlfriend.

FILM DESCRIPTION:
In this raunchy comedy, Josh (Breckin Meyer), a student at a college in Ithaca, NY, videotapes his one-night stand with beautiful sorority girl Beth (Amy Smart). A few days later, Josh discovers that one of his friends accidentally mailed the homemade porn tape to his girlfriend, Tiffany (Rachel Blanchard), who is spending some time with her family in Austin, TX. Josh and his friends Barry (Tom Green), Kyle (D.J. Qualls), E.L. (Seann William Scott), and Rubin (Paulo Costanzo) borrow a car and hit the road in a desperate bid to intercept the tape before Tiffany loads it into her VCR; Beth, however, wants Josh for herself and has her own plans to track down Tiffany. Road Trip is the first fiction feature from director Todd Phillips, noted for such edgy documentaries as Hated: G.G. Allin & the Murder Junkies, Screwed, and Frat House. The cast also includes Fred Ward and Andy Dick.

العجمي العجمان المري مره الوعيلي الوعله زامل جواب اسمع على مزاين هجيج الأبل الشاعر تركي بن فهد الميزاني 2000 الوايلي شاعر المليون المطيري العتيبي الدوسري القحطاني الحربي الرشيدي البقوم الهاجري دواسر قحطان حرب رشيد هاجر السبيعي السهلي زامل جواب ال حثلين ابو ساق ال نصيب مواجد متفائلون زاوج الشاعر صالح ال مانعه ال مطلق ال مخلص ال فروان ال فهاد ال عبدان ال غيدان مواجد ال نصيب بن حسين بن هضبان الصحراء السعوديه الكويت عمان البحرين قطر الأمارات أل سعود ال صباح ال ثاني ال خليفه ال الخليج عرب المختلف الساحه المحاوره الشعريه متفائلون  
المخيم الربيعي الثاني لملتقي يام لعام 2008 في دوله الكويت الذي قام به  رجل الأعمال:على بن فهد أل سالم العجمي
وذلك من أجل التعارف ما بين أبناءالقبيله ولم شمل أبناء القبيله ولنبذ الأرهاب من مجتمعنا وهو برعايه الأمير راكان بن خالد بن سحمان أل حثلين

العجمي العجمان المري مره الوعيلي الوعله زامل جواب اسمع على مزاين هجيج الأبل الشاعر تركي بن فهد الميزاني 2000 الوايلي شاعر المليون المطيري العتيبي الدوسري القحطاني الحربي الرشيدي البقوم الهاجري دواسر قحطان حرب رشيد هاجر السبيعي السهلي زامل جواب ال حثلين ابو ساق ال نصيب مواجد متفائلون زاوج الشاعر صالح ال مانعه ال مطلق ال مخلص ال فروان ال فهاد ال عبدان ال غيدان مواجد ال نصيب بن حسين بن هضبان الصحراء السعوديه الكويت عمان البحرين قطر الأمارات أل سعود ال صباح ال ثاني ال خليفه ال الخليج عرب المختلف الساحه المحاوره الشعريه متفائلون  
المخيم الربيعي الثاني لملتقي يام لعام 2008 في دوله الكويت الذي قام به  رجل الأعمال:على بن فهد أل سالم العجمي

snippet.description:
Hagamos un poco de conciencia sobre los animales ciegos...no los desprecies, no los abandones y obre todo no los sacrifiques, ellos no sufren y la ceguera en ellos es mas común de lo que te imaginas, no te asustes si tu perro queda ciego el podrá seguir haciendo su vida normal. La ceguera no es dolorosa y no es necesario poner a dormir a tu perro solo por el hecho de estar ciego. Para nosotros es doloroso ver a nuestro perro ciego, pero debemos rodearlo de emociones positivas.


• Haz énfasis en los sentidos que le quedan, un perro ciego se ayudará oliendo, oyendo, saboreando y sintiendo.

• Procura tratarlo de la forma más normal posible, trata de restaurar su confianza de que aún puede seguir haciendo cosas y que tú lo sigues queriendo ya que sigue siendo tu perro.

• No cambies de lugar sus muebles dentro de la casa, si tu perro está la mayor parte del tiempo dentro de ella.; lo mismo sucede con las cosas del patio si es que tu perro pasa la mayor parte del tiempo en él. Evita dejar obstáculos en el piso.

• Si tienes en tu casa alberca o cisterna y ésta no esta tapada colócales una barrera para prevenir que tu perro caiga dentro de ellas y muera ahogado por no poder encontrar las orillas.

• Saca a pasear a tu perro siempre con correa, recuerda que ahora tú eres su lazarillo, anticípate a los posibles problemas que se encuentre en el camino y condúcelo de forma clara, háblale mientras pasean, tu voz también le servirá de guía.

• Si alguna persona quiere saludar a tu mascota, pídele primero dejarse oler por el perro antes de tocarlo. La personalidad en la mayoría de los perros ciegos no cambia, pero algunos se pueden asustar y reaccionar mordiendo.

• Alimenta a tu perro y mantén su plato de agua siempre en el mismo lugar. Esta área se convertirá en un punto de referencia si tu mascota de pronto se desorientara.

• Después de comer o de usar sillas ponlas hacia adentro de la mesa o de los escritorios, las cosas que quedan saliendo estorban el camino, tu perro puede chocar con ellas y esta situación le producirá desorientación.

• Si de pronto tu mascota está desorientada, llévala a su cama o a su lugar de comida, esto le ayudará a reorientarse.

• Si tu casa es de dos plantas, colóca una barrera cerca de las escaleras hasta que tu perro se acostumbre a ellas, así evitará que por accidente éste caiga.

• La mayoría de los dueños de perros ciegos comentan que subir y bajar escaleras es lo más dificil de reaprender para un perro ciego. Se paciente, recuerda que tu perro está tratando de hacer su mejor esfuerzo.

• Si tienes otros perros en casa colócales campanas o cascabeles, esto ayudará a tu perro ciego a encontrarlos o a seguirlos, además de no asustarlo cuando se aproximen.

snippet.description:
2016 Cadillac CTS-V

Cadillac introduced the 2016 CTS-V, the most powerful product in the brand's 112-year history and the newest entry in the elite class of the world's highest-performing luxury cars.

Launching in late summer with 640 horsepower (477 kW), 630 lb-ft of torque (855 Nm) and a top speed of 200 mph, the new CTS-V reaches higher than its predecessors, leading Cadillac's product-driven expansion and elevation. It is the third generation of the acclaimed luxury sports sedan that launched the elite V-Series a decade ago - and redefined Cadillac for a new generation of enthusiasts. http://autoblackzone.com/

http://www.autoblackzone.com/
http://www.luweh.com/

"V-Series represents the very best of the Cadillac brand - the pinnacle of our design and technical capabilities," said Johan de Nysschen, Cadillac president. "The new CTS-V is the most compelling example of Cadillac's product substance and brand trajectory. The new CTS-V soars into the stratosphere of the most exhilarating luxury cars."

Comprehensive updates make the new CTS-V essentially two cars in one: a luxury sedan with sophisticated road manners and a track-capable sports car straight from the factory. It also introduces a new supercharged 6.2L V-8 engine backed by Cadillac's paddle-shift eight-speed automatic transmission, featuring launch control and Performance Algorithm Shifting.

With more horsepower and torque than the Mercedes-Benz 5.5L biturbo V-8 and the BMW M-series 4.4L TwinPower (twin-turbo) V-8, the new CTS-V is capable of 0-60 performance in 3.7 seconds.
http://luweh.com/
Track-honed design, chassis and suspension elements complement the supercharged powertrain and elevate CTS-V's capability, performance and driver control to new thresholds, while enabling track driving without modifications or special procedures. Key performance technologies include:

Standard carbon fiber hood and available carbon fiber vent, front splitter, rear spoiler and rear diffuser for greater aerodynamic performance
Brembo high-performance brake system developed to provide durability, consistency and the capability for track-day performance straight from the factory
Third-generation Magnetic Ride Control delivering 40-percent faster damping response
Integrated chassis controls that provide balanced performance for touring and the track, including competition-spec Performance Traction Management
Structural stiffness increased by 25 percent for improved ride and superior handling
Driver-selectable modes electronically calibrate performance variables for touring, sport and track driving conditions
Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with tri-compound technology offering excellent grip with extended wear
An interior with performance-oriented, sueded microfiber accents and matte-finish carbon fiber trim and available RECARO high-performance seats for spirited driving
Advanced safety and parking technologies, including a front curb-view camera system that provides a visual cue of curbs to protect the front splitter; automatic parking assist to find and steer into parallel or perpendicular parking spots; side blind zone alert, forward collision alert, lane keep assist and rear cross traffic alert.+

More powerful supercharged V-8 engine

The power behind the new CTS-V's capability is an all-new, more powerful 6.2L supercharged V-8 engine that makes more power more efficiently than the previous Cadillac supercharged engine. It employs a more-efficient, more-compact 1.7L supercharger and matches it with direct injection and Active Fuel Management (cylinder deactivation).

The supercharger's rotors are smaller in diameter than the previous supercharged engine, allowing higher maximum rpm that enables power-enhancing boost to be generated earlier in the rpm band. That boost is achieved more efficiently via a more direct discharge port that creates less turbulence, reducing heat and speeding airflow into the engine.

The Cadillac supercharged engine also has several unique features designed to support its high output and the greater cylinder pressures created by forced induction, including Rotocast A356T6 aluminum cylinder heads that are stronger and handle heat better than conventional aluminum heads, and lightweight titanium intake valves.

The CTS-V's complementing eight-speed automatic is tuned for world-class shift-response times. Smaller steps between gears keep the engine within the sweet spot of the rpm band, making the most of the output of the supercharged engine for exhilarating performance and greater efficiency.

The new 8L90 transmission offers full manual control via steering wheel paddles, and Performance Algorithm Shifting to deliver shift performance that rivals the dual-clutch/semi-automatic transmissions found in many luxury performance sedans - but with the smoothness and refinement that come with a conventional automatic fitted with a torque converter.

_______-----------------ABREME!!!!-------------------________
Hola guapisimas!!! Estoy feliz porque por fin pude grabar como pongo las uñas acrílicas, no soy una profesional y no digo que esta sea la forma correcta de aplicarlas, simplemente asi lo hago yo.

El pasado 28 de febrero fué el cumpleaños No. 18 de mi hermanita y me pidió que le regalara uñas (ademas de llevarla a un concierto de Camila jejejeje) y bueno este es el diseño que se nos ocurrió.

En verdad espero que les guste el resultado tanto como a mi y en verdad muchisimas gracias por todo su apoyo!! Les mando un abrazote a todas.

1) La canción como les dije en el video es HOTEL CALIFORNIA interpretada por The Killers del Album Rhythms del Mundo (Adoro este album!!!)

2) La imagen que aparece de fondo NO ES MIA la encontré en la pagina www.fabricsandpapers.com

3) No hago propaganda de ningun tipo a las marcas que uso, todos los productos que aparecen en el video los compré yo y no recibo nada a cambio de que aparezcan en mis videos.

snippet.description:
2009 gingen die Lichter in der Scania-Arena aus, was Duisburger Profieishockey angeht. Die Mission DEL ist beendet, ausschließlich letzte Plätze waren das Resultat. Doch trotzdem erfreuen sich die Fans großer Beliebheit in ganz Deutschland. Gewalt, Ausschreitungen und Gastfeindlichkeit, wie von manchen Eishockey "Ultra Crews" praktiziert (schönen Gruß nach Iserlohn), liegen Ihnen fern. Ob Sieg oder Niederlage, sie tragen ihre Farben Schwarz und Rot mit Stolz.
Dieses Video ist den Fans gewidmet. Tragt die Erinnerung in euren Herzen, doch lebt nicht in der Vergangenheit. Schaut nach vorn und beschränkt euch auf das, was uns wirklich wichtig ist: Aufrichtiges, ehrliches Eishockey. Ganz egal, ob in der Regionalliga oder sonst wo.

 *** Die Lieder sind und bleiben Eigentum der Künstler (Die Toten Hosen, Planlos), bzw. deren Labels und Vertreter ! ! ! *** 

*** special thanks to Julie for giving me the inspiration ***

snippet.description:
El Colegio Seminario, ubicado en San José Costa Rica es el principal Centro de Educación Privada del país. Cuenta con 118 años de existencia y ha tenido como estudiantes desde deportistas de los principales equipos de futbol y baloncesto, hasta religiosos, empresarios y ex-Presidentes de la República.

Los valores son la principal herramienta con la que cuentan sus alumnos para enfrentar a una sociedad cada vez más competitiva. Así mismo su categoría de Colegio Bilingüe y reconocido fortalecimiento de la Tecnología y Ciencia hacen de este centro de estudio un referente vital para quienes cursan sus estudios secundarios en Costa Rica.

Venga ... 

Acompáñenos en este Tour por los pasillos que por 5 años quizás usted recorrió a diario. Recuerde y deléitese ... porque el Colegio es la etapa más gratificante, gloriosa y especial de cada ser humano... y en las paredes, pasillos, aulas y canchas se guarda un recuerdo de usted ...

Bienvenidos !!

snippet.description:
The Couple
One of our last couples of 2011, Shawn + Satyma intimate yet grand set of events took place back in November. Starting from their big engagement party leading up to the wedding day and reception, everything about their wedding had something unique to offer.

Both of them are very close to their parents, especially Satyma being the only child of her parents. And we tried to capture that in our wedding film. 

Upon our first meeting, we realized that Satyma was very particular about everything while Shawn although seemed that way initially, wasn't so much by the end of the wedding. Shawn is a very calm and down to earth kind of a guy and compliments well with Satyma who is no different.

We had a great time capturing their special day. Here is their Next Day Edit



Technical Details

Two Canon 5D, Canon 60D
35 f1.4, 50 f1.2, 85 f1.2, 135 f2.0, 70-200 f2.8, 16-35 f2.8
Steadicam Merlin
Cinevate Atlas 10
Manfrotto Monopods

Zoom H4N

Adobe CS5

snippet.description:
The C.P. Company Goggle Jacket was originally designed by Massimo Osti as a gift, as part of C.P. Company's sponsorship involvement in the '988 edition of the iconic Mile Miglia (Thousand Miles) Italian open road endurance race. Its design features embody the cautious study of all functionality and innovation details derived from car racing. Its most original design features were the hinging goggles built into the hood and the window on the left sleeve through which a driver could check his watch whist driving. 

To celebrate 20 years since its release, C.P. Company invited RCA graduate (2006) Aitor Throup to re-invent this icon of clothing design, resulting in a forward-thinking ergonomic driving concept. 

Aitor Throup's design philosophy is centred around ideologies of a constant research to find new solution in clothing, mainly explored his own sculptures. Throup's 'justified design philosophy' dictates a need for a reason behind every design feature. His work has been described as 'conceptual functionalism'. The C.P. Company 20th anniversary Goggle Jacket is a direct example of this unique approach to design.

This exhibition (curated by Aitor Throup) incorporates the origins of the Goggle Jacket, as well as in-depth view into the design process and functionality behind the special 20th anniversary edition.

snippet.description:
In this the second half of the stall series, I deal with what should be the reaction of those who aren't losing inches or pounds for more than 4 weeks.  Note:  these are not for those that had a bad week or didn't lose in the last two week.

Here's a synopsis on what to try:
1. Take your measurements (make sure you are in a stall)
2. Start a food diary (Fitday, SparkPeople)
3. Evaluate what you are eating
4. Tweak exercise - "try 5"
5. Cut out certain groups (dairy, aspartame, caffiene, newly tried food groups)
6. Post your menu's at online support group sites
7. Fasting diet (Fat Fast or Stillman's Diet) for those with extreme metabolically resistance

snippet.description: Tosca is a 15 year-old medium Welsh gray pony mare. She is 13.1 and 1/8 hands high. Currently showing successfully in the Small/ Medium Childrens Pony Hunters. She got ribbons at the 2008 Hampton Classic in every class competing against 27 ponies. At the 2008 MHJ finals at Fieldstone Farm, Tosca and a 6 year-old won all 3 short stirrup hunter classes with 40 in the division. She was Champion. The pair also competed in the MHJ short stirrup medal final against 37, finishing 9th (the youngest rider at the show!). Shown in the Short Stirrup and Beginner Pre-Children's Equitation divisions for previous three years by an 8 year-old. Before that shown by my daughter Hannah (seen in pictures on the home page) when she was 9 and 10 years old in Pre-Childrens Pony Hunter. She was Reserve Grand Champion LIHSAA in 2005. Available for lease only. Go to karenimmerman.com for more information!

생긴 것만 '고프로'스러운 건지 중국이 실수(?)를 한 건지 봅시다.

SJCAM의 액션캠 SJ4000 WIFI(신형) VS Gopro Hero3+ Black Edition.
(비교 하다 보니 왠지 곧 출시 될 '고프로4'가 기대 되는 군요.)

이것에 대한 정식 리뷰는 11월쯤 오픈 할 엄스뮤직의
새로운 블로그(Blog)에서 보실 수 있으실 겁니다.

주소는 동일합니다.
http://eumsmusic.com

...하지만 궁금하잖아요? 짧게 하나만 적자면

SJ4000은 GoPro 와 같은 30FPS(1초에 30장) 임에도 불구하고 모션블러가 심합니다.
즉, 30장의 사진들의 셔터스피드?가 느리게 촬영된 느낌이 난다고 볼 수 있죠.
(영상의 흐름이 매끄럽지 못하고 잔상이 남은 듯한 어쩌면 끊기는 듯한 느낌)

그래서 장면이 움직이거나 빠른 피사체가 지나갈 때, SJ4000은 명확하게 캐치가 안 됩니다.
반면 고프로는 전체적으로 스무스한 영상 흐름을 보여주죠. 이게 바로 퀄리티 차이.

================================

http://www.eumsmusic.com
↑ eumsmusic blog.

http://www.facebook.com/eumsmusic
↑ eums facebook.

* Drummer - Joowon Eum(드러머 엄주원)
_Bosphorus cymbals ENDOSER(Artist).
_Aquarian Heads ENDOSER(Artist).
_Gretsch drums ENDOSER(Artist).
_GoPro Hero Cam Korean Artist(KOL).
_Support by AXIS Drum Pedals.

www.OrganicEarthJewlery.com - Organic Earth Jewelry™ - Handcrafted, Organic Coconut Earrings, Bracelets, Necklaces and Rings

The coconuts and palm nuts used to hand-carve our organic coconut jewelry are acquired from local farmers in Mexico and South America. What is not pressed for coconut oil is utilized for this form of art and income. At Kelley's Cache we work directly with all artisans producing our organic jewelry line, using natural materials that are often recycled or reclaimed. Your purchase significantly helps improve the quality of life of traditional carvers, artisans and their families, while preserving their tribal art and culture.

snippet.description: This is the first video I have EVER edited, so its nothing near perfect.  Its a quick video of the build up of my 92 LX Coupe. Started as a 4cyl/auto car that I converted to a 5.0/T5/Mass Air Car.... Did all myself but the rebuild of the motor and trans. The car is a stock displacement/compression ratio 302 with a GT40 Intake, 70mm MAF, 24lb. Injectors, 70mm TB, BBK Fenderwell Intake, Underdrive Pulleys, X-Cam, Comp Hi-tech Pushrods, Comp Dual Valve Springs, Proform 1.6 Aluminum Roller Rockers (suck), Cheap Flo Tech Long Tube Headers, KYB AGX Adjustable Front Struts, Cut Ford Racing Front Drag Springs, QA1 Tubular K-member, Sub-frame Connectors, FRPP Aluminum Driveshaft, BMR Upper and Lower Control Arms, Rear Lakewood Drag Shocks, and a bunch of other stuff I'm sure I'm missed.... The color is Olive Drab Green and its temporary until I can do the body work and the final paint job. Just wanted it one color and something other than Flat black or Primer Grey.  The car is slow, but its mine and I love it.... Its a blast to drive!! Enjoy.

Cox Channel 11 and Cox Communications Virginia present the Homecoming of the USS Mahan.

The guided-missile destroyer USS Mahan (DDG 72) returns to Naval Station Norfolk, Va., Wednesday, June 8, after completing a seven-month deployment to the Horn of Africa and the Sixth Fleet area of responsibility.

While on deployment, the ship conducted maritime security operations and theater security operations to promote long-term regional stability, prevent conflict, and protect U.S. and coalition interests.

snippet.description:
The 2013 Tour de France saw the arrival of the Focus Izalco Chrono. We took a look at Romain Bardet's time trial machine.
Subscribe to GCN on YouTube: http://gcn.eu/gcnsubs

Romain Bardet of Ag2r was the leading French finisher at the 2013 Tour de France, placing 15th overall. We took a look at his brand new time trial bike.

The Focus may fit within the UCI regulations, but, at the same time, it stretches them as far as possible.

Bardet's rig is equipped with Campagnolo Record mechanical throught. He chooses a 54 tooth chainring and 11-23 cassette. There are nods to aerodynamics throughout his component choice, with Campagnolo's aerodynamic Bora Ultra chainset and Look Keo Blade Aero pedals.

Music: Organtronics - Astoria: http://gcn.eu/18OM6I8

About GCN:

The Global Cycling Network puts you in the centre of the action: from the iconic summit of the Stelvio to the epic trails of Fort William, Scotland, everywhere there is pavé or dirt, world-class racing, and pro riders, we will be there bringing you all the action, essential analysis and unparalleled access every week, every month, and every year.

Welcome to the Global Cycling Network | Inside cycling

3) a heavy cannot stand up again if he crouches while you are on his head

snippet.description:
※ローバーミニが持つ独特の魅力

〆:ローバーミニは1959年8月に、アレック・イシゴニスによって開発され、基本ボディーはそのままに約40年以上も製造され続けられたイギリスの車です。

《 ミニのディープな世界に飛び込め！ 》

〆:ローバーミニの魅力は、クラッシックなスタイルと、乗り心地、そしてアフターパーツの多さだと思います。

〆:スタイル的には、現代の車にはない雰囲気があげられ、ボディサイズ的には軽自動車より一回り小さいのも魅力の一つと言えるでしょう。（車幅に限ってはオーバーフェンダーによっては大きくなりますが...）

◇ミニの魅力の乗り心地は、ゴーカートにのっているようで、それを魅力と思える世界です!!

一番の理由はサスペンションの材質にあり、今、世界中の車の大多数にサスペンションにはスプリングが採用されていて（エアサスもありますが...）、ローバーミニはラバーコーンが使われています。
ラバーコーン（ゴムの塊）の材質は、路面のデコボコは、ダイレクトにガンガン車内にまで伝わってきます。
あとはミニオーナーの醍醐味とも言えるアフターパーツですが、かなりのパーツがあり、資金次第で限りなく自分仕様に仕上げることができると思います。
現在も、新しいパーツは次々新発売されています。
もちろん、定番のパーツも入手でき、ビンテージスタイルもオリジナルスタイルも対応できる環境にあると言えるでしょう。

〆:ローバーミニの製造が終わり、すでに10年以上が経ち、ローバーミニと言う車は世の中から減って行くしかありません。
ならば今現状残っているミニを残せるように、ミニファンが増えてくれればと...思います。

 KingsRoad Depot:HP
http://www.kingsroad32.com/
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""" 
♪BGM＝タイトル：I Believe In Love
♪=季節のアーティスト：Barry White
ジャンル：R&B/8:06
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
「気の向くままの散歩道」ユッキーの部屋

話題性のある出来事や面白話、それにユニークなものまで、少しでも視聴された方が、ひと時の憩い所になればと・・・

Self-introduction

I would like to tell you the pleasant talk which I experienced.

snippet.channelTitle: Sofia Talvik - Swedish Americana Artist & Songwriter
snippet.description:
Download album: http://music.sofiatalvik.com/
Artist: Sofia Talvik
http://music.sofiatalvik.com
Album: Blue Moon
Track: #02 Ghosts

Sofia Talvik is releasing her debut album Blue Moon on YouTube. The album is completely interactive with a menu of the songs  that makes it easy to browse trough the album.

Please subscribe to the channel if you like the music!
--

Sofia Talvik was born on an island just off the west coast of Sweden. Her debut album Blue Moon took forty intense hours to record and the end result is a collection of songs presented virtually intact from the original live studio sessions.

Having earn a reputation as a great live performer, frequently playing at clubs in and around Stockholm and throughout Sweden, this is naturally the only way of bringing Sofia's gentle, almost fragile voice to you and gives the album a unique sound, making it almost timeless in the sense that it could have been recorded twenty years ago as well as twenty years from now.

Blue Moon was released in May 2005, and got rave reviews from press all over Sweden.

Released 26 January 2005
Produced by Sofia Talvik
All music and lyrics by Sofia Talvik 

Copyright by Makaki Music

Hey everyone, today I am doing a collaboration with Elena from LaineyLoops. We decided to create a look based off Nina Dobrev's two characters in The Vampire Diaries, I am doing Katherine, while Elena is doing Elena

The thing with Katherine's makeup is she is like the night time version of Elena's makeup, she tends to smoke it up.I have seen her in the show, with a less dramatic look that I have created, but I wanted to go with Katherine's more vampy eye look. Usually Katherine has a soft muted lip, so I have gone in with a nude shade. 

I filmed a voice over, as I have a sore throat at the moment, so apologies for sounding horrible lol. 

Leave me a comment below telling me your fave Katherine moment.

Apple USB Superdrive Review
Detail product - http://bit.ly/1Wei484

Compact and convenient, the Apple USB SuperDrive connects to your MacBook Pro with Retina display, MacBook Air, or Mac mini with a single USB cable and fits easily into a travel bag. It lets you install software and play and burn both CDs and DVDs, including double-layer DVDs.
Features:
Everything you need in an optical drive. Whether you're at the office or on the road, you can play and burn both CDs and DVDs with the Apple USB SuperDrive. It's perfect when youwant to watch a DVD movie, install software, create backup discs, and more.
Take it anywhere. Only slightly bigger than a CD case, the Apple USB SuperDrive slips easily into your travel bag when you hit the road and takes up little space on yourdesk or tray table when you're working.
The essence of simplicity. You'll never have to worry about lost cables with the Apple USB SuperDrive. Itconnects to your MacBook Pro with Retina display,MacBook Air, or Mac mini with a single USB cable that's built into the SuperDrive. There's no separate power adapter, and it works whether your Mac is plugged in or running on battery power.

snippet.description:
Fases:
Colina Vainilla 3:
Nada más comenzar la fase, ve a la derecha donde vas a una plataforma formada por calaveras. Sube a ella y ve a la derecha del todo hasta que llegues a una tubería. Pégate a ella y salta para descubrir un bloque secreto en el que te tienes que apoyar para avanzar. Luego tienes que seguir yendo hacia la derecha por el único camino posible, hasta que llegas a la meta que te hace completar la fase.

Colina Vainilla 4:
Lo único que tienes que hacer es llegar a la derecha del todo, pero es un poco complicado, ya que de vez en cuando aparecen unas balas de cañón que van hacia ti. Además hay zonas en las que tienes que saltar por las ramas para poder avanzar.

PAROLES

REFRAIN X2

C'est nous les héros, c'est eux les p'tites merdes
On fait partie de la génération sans pète
Naïfs par nature, des cœurs noircis par l'herbe
S'ils croient nous la mettre, ils n'ont rien vu frère !

COUPLET 1

On a tué personne, ni sauvé la vie à quiconque
Arrêtez l'scénar', welcome dans le vrai, tire le rideau !
Faut de la patience, la vie met des coups 
Si épreuve il y a 
C'est pour voir qui d'entre nous doute, ce que coûtent
Les convictions et de rester vrai 
On s'en fout de leurs histoires, on a peur du second acte
Halal, haram, trop jactent, j'enfile mes boules Quies 
Si Dieu pitch nos life c'était le destin
La rue c'est pas ma mère donc 
J'l'a fait tapiner, respect aux anciens 
Le monde ne s'arrête pas au quartier
C'est nous les héros malgré nos béquilles
Nos cœurs sont rouges vifs, on encaisse, on enquille 
On perd des braves, la mort n'a plus l'effet de rappel
Nos vies sont des films et souvent j'me cogne la tête
Ici poto, c'est la rapacité qui règne 
J'honore les miens, plus 2pac que 2chainz 

REFRAIN X2

C'est nous les héros, c'est eux les p'tites merdes
On fait partie de la génération sans pète
Naïfs par nature, des cœurs noircis par l'herbe
S'ils croient nous la mettre, ils n'ont rien vu frère !

COUPLET 2

J'suis de la ville où a joué Valderrama
Laurent Blanc et l'col monté d'Eric Cantona
Si on nous cantonne à nos rôles de 
Délinquants de cité c'est pour nous occuper
Pendant qu'ils font les gros sous frère !
Pour tout refaire faudrait un syphon 
Ainsi font les marionnettes qui 
Finiront chiffons, bien sûr 
Qu'on a des regrets, c'est la course aux biffons
Rester vrai, mettre un strike, baraka des parents
On veut pas de chef, on veut des millions 
Pas de qualification 
On veut soulever la coupe du monde 
Pour pas péter la boule, allume le radar de recul
Pour ne pas rater son coup, s'occuper d'son cul
Joue pas trop les grands frères, ça marche pas si tu titubes
On a vu "La Haine" et la fin du regretté Cousin Hub'
J'ai saigné sur l'asphalte pour des valeurs
J'ai arraché l'asphalte pour l'honneur, chope ça !

REFRAIN X2

C'est nous les héros, c'est eux les p'tites merdes
On fait partie de la génération sans pète
Naïfs par nature, des cœurs noirci par l'herbe
S'ils croient nous la mettre, ils n'ont rien vu frère !

On saurait se satisfaire d'un milliard ou des minimas sociaux
L'argent fait le bonheur mais les problèmes n'en finissent pas
Une main qui tend ne sera jamais une main qui donne
Il faut faire du pognon pour n'avoir aucune raison de s'plaindre
La France se rappellera de ceux nés en 88
On a les morts, on est enfermés en vie
Toutes les disquettes sur l'Islam et tout leur racisme
Montrent que la France n'est plus souveraine dans son pays !

OUTRO

Chope ça ! C'est nous les héros, c'est eux les p'tites merdes
Ils se rappelleront de nous nés en 88
Chope ça ! Arashsfalte missile
On a compris leurs magouilles, etcetera...
Le seul moyen de s'en sortir aujourd'hui c'est de se souder un minimum, un minimum
Et viser l'mille et ne pas se tromper d'ennemis...
Ch-chope ça !

snippet.description: Co uděláte, aby se Vaše 25 let stará platonická láska stala skutečnou? Možná všechno a možná nic, možná zjistíte, že to, co se za 25 let nestihlo, se už nezvládne Sněženky a machři jdou ve stopách životů hlavních hrdinů v době, která všechno změnila. Jak prošli jejími nástrahami a jaké šrámy to na nich zanechalo? Kam chtěli jít, kam došli a kam ještě dojdou? Jsme opět na horské chatě, kde se všichni po letech scházejí a opět zažijí mnoho nezapomenutelných chvil. Na horách se setkávají někdejší spolužáci, aby se viděli, aby si zavzpomínali a aby sami sebe ujistili v tom, že to s nimi ještě není tak hrozné, protože ty někdejší holky a kluky si stále nesou v sobě. Co na tom, že už uběhlo mnoho let, co na tom, že se změnil svět i všichni účastníci někdejšího lyžařského kurzu, z něhož se časem stala legenda. V kinech od 18.12.2008.

snippet.description:
Requested by Hnthal

facebook - https://www.facebook.com/Pinsetter1991

This is the first full manga drawing I have ever done. I did a Google search for this guy "The Fourth Hokage", found a picture, and drew it...but now that I go back and look at other pictures of him, I don't think the one I drew looks a whole lot like him haha. So I might do another one that looks more like him, but hey Its still manga, I think Its alright.

SONG free download- http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/334683

Materials: (all can be found at Michaels, Aaron Bro's, Jo-ann fabrics, or online)
Generals charcoal pencils and compressed charcoal sticks
2B and 8B Staedtler Mars Lumograph graphite pencils (the 8B is used the most)
Clic retractable eraser and a Faber Castell pencil eraser
Vellum Bristol Paper (wausau)
Pink Pearl erasers
Blending sticks - stubs - tortillions and a small blending chamois
Recorded with a Brinno Timelapse cam
Edited with Windows Movie Maker 2.6

Final Image- http://pinsetter1991.deviantart.com/#/d2qvzd5

-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NPL626VFNHw
-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-

Presentamos el tráiler cinemático oficial de Mists of Pandaria, la cuarta expansión de World of Warcraft, que debutó en la gamescom 2012 el pasado 16 de agosto en Colonia, Alemania. Si deseas más información sobre esta enorme actualización de la aclamada franquicia de World of Warcraft —incluyendo opciones de compra— visita: http://blizzard.com/games/mists/?int=wow

Descubre los misterios de Pandaria
Pusiste fin a la destructiva furia de Alamuerte y salvaste a los vuelos de los dragones de la extinción. Ahora deberás descubrir los misterios del continente perdido y revelar los oscuros secretos del pasado de Pandaria. Explora reinos ancestrales ocultos desde el Hendimiento, obtén vastos tesoros en las profundidades de bóvedas olvidadas y defiende Pandaria de la sombra de un mal enterrado por largo tiempo; antes de que sea demasiado tarde.

snippet.description:
Auch in Call of Duty Ghosts ist die NUKE, MOAB oder der (wie in Ghosts genannt) KEM-Strike wieder zu finden. (Atomarer Atomschlag kleiner Innsider Witz um die guten alten Zeiten Willen)

Das ganze ist in einer privaten Lobby aufgenommen, da ich als ich es Online herausgefunden habe, nicht auf "Aufnahme" gedrückt hatte, hehe (ich depp)

Im Multiplayer selbstverständlich möglich.

VIELEN DANK AN MR BUD SPENCER, der mir geholfen hat, das Video aufzunehmen. Schaut auch bei ihm vorbei unter dem Namen XboxDome (XboxDome.de) 
Wie kriegt man ihn am besten?
Dazu gibt es zweierlei Möglichkeiten:

1. 25-Kill Serie (ohne zu sterben)
2. Im Video beschrieben (für diejenigen die es flotter haben möchten)

Der KEM-Strike ist nur unter bestimmten Umständen möglich, auf bestimmten Karten, in bestimmten Bereichen der Karte.

Das war die Möglichkeit die ich herausgefunden habe ( VORERST!!! )
Ich werde mich definitiv auf die Suche begeben um weiteres für euch zu finden.

Bis dahin....
Still gestanden, Abonniert und weggetreten.

Sergeant Offbeat

*Note 2 Tips & Tricks Table of Contents: http://tinyurl.com/b64yfs2

I finally got the S Note update for the Samsung Galaxy Note 2 that I've gotten many questions about.  At first glace, it is a bit confusing why some features were removed and added from the original S Note.  But there is a reason to the madness, and in this video I explain what the new S Note is and what it isn't.  

I also cover, in-depth, the new features, what you don't get compared to the Note 3's S Note, and when you should use the new S Note over the original S Note which you will still need.

Full Article: http://www.TheDailyNote.Net/2014/03/samsung-galaxy-note-2-tips-tricks.html

Music used in this channel was downloaded from YouTube Creation Tools
Track: Gympsy Dance (background), Path to Follow (outro)

The graphical intro and outro was purchased from intromaker.NET. The license covers video streaming on websites including YouTube and also covers merging it with my own material.

I also cover, in-depth, the new features, what you don't get compared to the Note 3's S Note, and when you should use the new S Note over the original S Note which you will still need.

Elektromobilität: Nicht erst seit den deutlich steigenden Spritpreisen ein Thema. 
Die ersten serienmäßig gebauten Autos aus Europa sind seit kurzem ja schon haben - auch wenn die Batterieleistung derzeit nur für kurze Strecken reicht.
Aber wie sieht es eigentlich mit Elektroflugzeugen aus? Bislang stand die Luftfahrt immer in dem Ruf, laut zu sein und jede Menge Abgase zu produzieren. Wie gesagt: bislang. Denn ein Erfinder aus Nesselwang hat heute auf der Luftfahrtmesse aero in Friedrichshafen seinen Prototyp für Co2 neutrales Fliegen vorgestellt.

snippet.description:
Nacido en Ticumán Morelos. Su nombre de pila Omar Castillo, su nombre en los ruedos "El Güero de Ticumán".

Comienza sus primeras montas en el año de 1994,  inicia al estilo lazo castigando con las espuelas al cincho. En una de estas jugadas en la plaza de Ahuatepec Morelos, recibe un golpe muy fuerte en el parpado izquierdo que lo deja marcado para siempre, sin embargo esto no lo doblega y continua en este trabajo rudo, y logra perfeccionar el estilo grapa dominándolo al 100%,logrando montas espectaculares. Esto le dio muchas satisfacciones y muchos premios. Con ello se convierte en uno de los jinetes más queridos y ovacionados por el público conocedor del buen jaripeo en diferentes plazas de la republica mexicana.

La plaza de toros "La Guadalupana" de Cuautla Morelos es el escenario donde se lleva a cabo el torneo del cougar aquí participa "el Güero de Ticumán" y gana su primer torneo montando el toro "el taquillero" de Abundio Mendoza de rancho los cedros.

Hizo campeones a muchos otros toros como:

La cola de plata de Joan Sebastián

El señor de las canas de Adán Velásquez

El diputado de Amado Orihuela.

El 16 de octubre del 2000 monta el toro el candidato de Joan Sebastián en la plaza de toros la predilecta de Taxco Guerrero.

Domingo 13 de mayo del 2001 participa en el gran torneo rey de reyes en san José Tejalpa.

Domingo 4 de Noviembre del 2001 gana un torneo en Villa Guerrero Edomex. Se impone a los mejores jinetes, Ruso de Zapata, Aguilita de Zepayautla, Caballo de Jalisco y Bitoque de Tenancingo.

Domingo 19 de Marzo del 2002 ganó un torneo mas en San José Tejalpa, enfrentando a Chino Guerrero (EPD), Chícharo García, Zarco de Puente, Cachas de oro y Caballo de Jalisco.

Ganador de las espuelas de plata, ganador de torneos de centenarios, ganador de automóviles.

Enfrentó 6 ocasiones el Toro con mentalidad casi humana "El huracán" logrando 4 quedas y sintió el rigor de 2 porrazos.

Su último torneo el 31 de marzo del 2002 montando al toro "el turbo" de Querétaro, una jugada espectacular y lucida en todo lo alto, logrando con ello el triunfo del torneo.

El momento trágico el 20 de Abril del 2002 en la plaza de toros "Emiliano Zapata Salazar" de Anenecuilco Morelos, participa en este jaripeo a beneficio de una escuela primaria. Monta por segunda ocasión al toro "el Devastador" de Nacho Castro. Quien iba a imaginar que esta sería la última pagina de su libro, Omar Castillo "EL Güero de Ticumán" muere bajo las patas del toro, después de haber colgado peligrosamente, muere el hombre de manera muy dramática.

Muere el hombre pero nace el recuerdo, y su nombre hace eco en cada rincón donde gusta el jaripeo.

Descanse en paz....Omar Castillo "El Güero de Ticumán"

In an era of rapid change in media and technology, the not-for-profit Paley Center for Media explores the evolving ways in which we create, consume, and connect through media. snippet.description:
Der schöne Pascha (1619_A_12) ist nun schon etwas länger im Tierheim. Sein Verhalten hat sich sehr positiv verändert. Er sitzt jetzt in einer Hundegruppe mit Hündinnen und Rüden, dort verhält er sich sehr sozial und vorbildlich. Er ist nicht auf Streit aus, geht sogar ernsthaften Auseinandersetzungen souverän aus dem Weg. Fremden gegenüber ist er zwar noch etwas misstrauisch, das legt sich aber schnell. Es ist eine Freude  Pascha beim Spielen zu beobachten, er läuft dem Stöckchen hinterher bringt es  und gibt es auf Kommando ab. Auch mit dem Ball spielt er super gerne.
Wenn man bedenkt, dass dieser Hund vor ein paar Wochen noch seine Besitzer an geknurrt,  Autos und Fahrräder verbellt hat, ist ein toller Bursche aus ihm geworden.
Auf Grund seines Temperaments sollten keine kleinen Kinder im Haushalt leben, die wären überfordert.
Dieser junge Hund braucht eine klare und konsequente Führung.
Die neuen Besitzer sollten in einem ruhigen Umfeld leben und souveräne, erfahrene Menschen sein.
Wer meint, für Pascha den richtigen Platz zu haben, sollte einfach mal ins Tierheim kommen.

Musik : http://www.dreamweaver.at

Suprise! LOl xD This is a TOTALLY made-up series... Just used their real names:D
PLOT:
Vanessa has moved to US from France, where she was a professional dancer.
She got a part in movie, "Nightmare", which has always been a dream of her.
When she is to visit her friend in San Lous Obispo, she meets Zac, and they have immadietley a great chemistry, but they never knew they'd meet again.
But they accidently keeps meeting, and eventually get together. 
But Vanessa don't know who Zac really is, one of the biggest stars in Hollywood. And when she dounds out, and the world founds about them, everything changes...

Ok, I know I have "Hate to Love"  and so you know, for a couple of weeks ago, I made all the episodes up to 10, and I was about to send them up quick, like a suprise. Then I realized that I couldn't upload them, they were to big (Over 100 MB, I use alot of effects). So I just.. I dunno, I ost the willing. So I've been writing on this, and I'm really excited!
Hope yo like it... The first episode WILL be out soon!
//Aly

snippet.description:
Sneaky Captain Hook has frozen the water to try and capture the mermaid's treasure, however Captain Frost arrives with Jake and the rest of his crew to try and stop him, will they be able to recover the mermaid's treasure?

Welcome to the official Disney Junior UK YouTube channel! Disney Junior is the place where magical storytelling comes to life. Watch clips and get ready to sing-a-long to songs from your little one’s favourite shows including Doc McStuffins, Sofia The First, The Lion Guard, Captain Jake and the Never Land Pirates, PJ Masks, Miles From Tomorrow, Mickey Mouse Clubhouse, Henry Hugglemonster, Sheriff Callie and Minnie’s Bow-Toons.

Subscribe to get a new dose of DisneyJuniorUK fun every day! ► http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=disneyjunioruk 

Watch more videos on DisneyJuniorUK! ► 
Official site: http://www.disney.co.uk/disney-junior/

Like Disney Junior UK on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/disneyjuniorUK

Follow @DisneyJuniorUK on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/DisneyJuniorUK/

Follow @DisneyJuniorUK on Twitter: http://twitter.com/DisneyJuniorUK 

Jake and the Never Land Pirates follows the adventures of Jake and his crew as he looks to collect gold doubloons in Never Land. Inspired by characters and the magical land behind the second star to the right in the Disney Classic Peter Pan, Jake and the Never Land Pirates features classic characters like Mr. Smee and Captain Hook who often get in the way of Jake’s plans. It’s always an adventure with Jake and his crew!

Jake and the Never Land Pirates has some fantastic songs to sing-a-long to including the theme song Yo Ho Lets Go, Captain Hook (Is a Cranky Crook), Talk like a Pirate and Roll up the Map!

JAKE AND THE NEVER LAND PIRATES CHARACTER LIST

• JAKE –  Jake looks to collect as many gold doubloons as possible on each of his adventures. Often the one saving the day, Jake is both brave, skilled with a sword and an excellent friend to his crew mates. 

• IZZY – Not only is Izzy Jake’s best friend and member of the crew, but she also had a little bag of pixie dust that can help the gang out of tricky situations when she says “Pixie dust away!” Izzy often likes to react to trouble when she says “Yay hey no way!”

• CUBBY – Although Cubby’s the youngest member of the crew, it doesn’t mean he doesn’t have as much responsibility! Cubby is an excellent navigator and has a map of Never Land to help the gang around the island. Cubby’s catchphrase is “Aww Coconuts!” which he’ll often use when trouble arises. 

• SKULLY – As Jake’s parrot friend, Skully does his best to look after the whole team and keep a watchful eye from the sky whilst they’re on their adventures. 

• CAPTAIN JAMES HOOK – You’ll probably recognize Captain Hook from Peter Pan as the baddy or the villain of Never Land, which is also still true in Captain Jake and the Never Land Pirates. Hook will often refer to Jake and his crew as the ‘popinjays’ especially when they’re getting in the way of him getting his own way! Captain Hook loves treasure and sails aboard the Jolly Rodger looking out for the popinjays getting in the way of his plans.

• MR. SMEE – Sidekick to Captain Hook, Mr. Smee often gets called a ‘blundering idiot’ for not doing as Hook told him to do or for letting the popinjays get away. Mr. Smee looks up to Captain Hook but is also scared of upsetting him. Mr. Smee has a kind heart really and will often help Hook see the error in his way. 

• SHARKY & BONES – Whilst members of Captain Hook’s crew, they won’t often help all that much in Captain Hook’s plans. Sharky & Bones are normally too interested in singing a song or grand musical number.

snippet.description:
平成２６年９月２２日１７時出発途中高舘サービスエリアに立ち寄り車中泊仕様にしたエスティマハイブリッドにて仮眠、第一目的地である青森県上北鉱山跡まで５５キロなので４時に出発し目的地には５時到着。ここ迄の道は他の方の記事とか読むと普通車では行かない方が良いと書いて有りましたが砂利道ですが平均２０キロ程で走れる道でした。明るくなるのを待って撮影しましたが早朝という事で従業員の方は居ないみたいでしたが勝手に敷地内に入っては駄目なので道路からの離着陸としました。結構高低差が有り奥行もあるので慎重に飛ばしました。この夏は廃鉱山跡を何か所か撮影しましたがここは２番目に良い所でした。
普通は下手なのをカバーする為にスロー再生させる人も居るみたいですが、今回はたくさんの映像を見て欲しい事から０分１２秒以降は２倍速としています。速度を速めるとブレ（揺れ）が目立ってしまいます（泣）。

平成２６年９月２２日１７時出発途中高舘サービスエリアに立ち寄り車中泊仕様にしたエスティマハイブリッドにて仮眠、第一目的地である青森県上北鉱山跡まで５５キロなので４時に出発し目的地には５時到着。ここ迄の道は他の方の記事とか読むと普通車では行かない方が良いと書いて有りましたが砂利道ですが平均２０キロ程で走れる道でした。明るくなるのを待って撮影しましたが早朝という事で従業員の方は居ないみたいでしたが勝手に敷地内に入っては駄目なので道路からの離着陸としました。結構高低差が有り奥行もあるので慎重に飛ばしました。この夏は廃鉱山跡を何か所か撮影しましたがここは２番目に良い所でした。
普通は下手なのをカバーする為にスロー再生させる人も居るみたいですが、今回はたくさんの映像を見て欲しい事から０分１２秒以降は２倍速としています。速度を速めるとブレ（揺れ）が目立ってしまいます（泣）。

Here is a very quick video on how to change the boot logo on your iPod Touch or iPhone with RedSn0w without completely rejailbreaking!  No restore is required, all you need is a Jailbroken iPod Touch or iPhone on firmware 3.1.3, and this should be very easy for you!
----------------------------------------------------------
Supported devices are the iPod Touch 1G, iPod Touch 2G (NON MC), the iPhone 1G (Known as iPhone 2G), and the iPhone 2G (Known as the iPhone 3G).

Unsupported devices include the iPod Touch 2G (MC MODEL), the iPod Touch 3G, and the iPhone 3GS, both old bootrom and new bootrom, neither work.
------------------------------------------------
Below are the links for RedSn0w:

These links are for iPhone 2G,3G & iPod Touch 1st Generation ONLY!

Windows:
http://xs1.iphwn.org/rs//redsn0w-win_0.9.2.zip

Mac:
http://xs1.iphwn.org/rs/redsn0w-mac_0.9.2.zip

These links are for iPod Touch 2nd Generation (NON MC) ONLY!

Windows:
http://xs1.iphwn.org/redsn0w-win_0.9.4.zip

Mac:
http://xs1.iphwn.org/redsn0w-mac_0.9.4.zip
---------------------------------------------------------
This is where to download the 3.1.2 firmware: http://www.felixbruns.de/iPod/firmware/
----------------------------------------------------
Here are the custom boot logos (PNG Format NEEDED): http://www.google.com/images?q=custom+iphone+boot+logos&oe=utf-8&rls=org.mozilla:en-US:official&client=firefox-a&um=1&ie=UTF-8&source=og&sa=N&hl=en&tab=wi&biw=1280&bih=606
----------------------------------------------------
Please subscribe to my second Youtube channel: http://www.youtube.com/user/OTHERdahacker13

Please follow me on Twitter: http://twitter.com/dahacker13

And lastly, thanks for watching the video, please rate it five stars, leave a comment, and don't forget to subscribe ;)

snippet.description:
Superman und Batman möchten ganz wie die Konkurrenz von Marvel ein Team aus Superhelden gründen, um dem Bösen ein für alle Male das Handwerk zu legen und Frieden und Wohlstand in der Welt zu gewährleisten. Aber Rom wurde ja auch nicht an einem Tag erbaut. Der erste Schritt ist also eine gemeinsame WG in der Festung der Einsamkeit, da Batman die ganze Fahrerei ziemlich auf den Zeiger geht. Und da wären wir auch schon bei den alltäglichen Problemen, die so eine WG mit sich bringt...

In der heutigen Episode bringt Batman einen neuen Robin mit zur Festung der Einsamkeit. Doch Superman ist nicht wirklich überzeugt...

Let's Play - Clash of Clans - Episode 6 from SimonVideo.com HD - Apple iOS App Reviews. Like this? Watch the latest episode of SimonVideo.com HD - Apple iOS App Reviews on Blip! http://blip.tv/simonvideo/watch 

Todayapos;s episode shows how I changed some of the positions of my towers to balance them up and wall up two islands on the left  right of my village. And a attack using barbarian, archer, goblins, healer, giant and wall breakers. 

I love healing spell and rage spell...not sure why but it did helped me tremendously but yes it does cost a lot but in event of high resource raids...why leave it to chance? 

Hmmm The reason why I have low resources and slow upgrades because I have a balance life, I don't play coc every waking hour of my day and I donapos;t waste gems on coc hehe. I am not sure if rearranging my buildings will yield sucess or not but so far itapos;s pretty encouraging. :D

snippet.description:
Graffiti is not the sort of thing you would think about preserving.  But what if that graffiti was from a historical moment in time that many current college students were not alive to see?

The Berlin Wall fell in 1989, and Rice University's Baker Institute has been home to a section of the Berlin Wall since 2000. Over the years the original graffiti on Rice's Berlin Wall monument has faded.  Art conservators are periodically hired to restore the original messages from the peaceful reunification of Germany.   

Standing 14 feet high and weighing over two tons, the steel-reinforced concrete slab was donated to Rice by Browning-Ferris Industries of Houston.  The monument was removed from the section that separated West Berlin's Frohnau District from the East German district of Oranienburg.

QUE ME QUITEN LA VIDA . . PERO NO LA ESPERANZA.
UNA VIDA SIN ESPERANZA ES UN DESIERTO SIN OASIS . . . TODA LA ESTRUCTURA ESPIRITUAL HUMANA ESTÁ BASADA EN LA ESPERANZA . . . ES LA RESPUESTA ENTRE LA VIDA Y EL POR QUÉ SE VIVE . . . SÓLO SE NECESITA LA LUZ QUE ILUMINE EL CAMINO QUE CONDUCE, ENTRE LA SOLIDEZ DE LAS PIEDRAS Y LO MÍSTICO DEL ALMA, HACIA DONDE ELLA HABITA . . . 
EL AMOR ES EL SUEÑO ALCANZABLE QUE VINCULA MATERIA Y ESPÍRITU . . . SURGE CON LA VIDA Y NO TERMINA CON LA MUERTE PORQUE ES SUPERIOR A LA MAGNITUD TIEMPO-ESPACIO . . . LOS SERES HUMANOS NO TIENEN LA EDAD DE LOS AÑOS . . . POSEEN LA EDAD DE SU CORAZÓN . . . CUÁNTO HAS AMADO . . . CUÁNTO HAS VIVIDO . . . NACER ES CASUAL . . . MORIR IMPOSIBLE . . . EL AMOR NOS HACE ETERNOS . . . ES SIEMPRE UNA OPORTUNIDAD . . . ES LA CONTINUIDAD INFINITA . . . LA MÁS SUBLIME EXPRESIÓN DE VIDA . . . EN SUS DIFERENTES MANIFESTACIONES . . .

snippet.description:
Free 7 Track album : http://www.cockrockdisco.net/releases/digital/crockp3-041

It's time for a new sound and Melt Unit has it.  Here's 7 tracks packed with speed and inspired by classic jungle, but with a contemporary twist that feels both refreshing and infectious. It's as if the often discussed "potential" of re-visiting the Drum and Bass past finally became the futuristic present where each slamming snare collides with an image identity born and raised in post-media pop. All genres are present, yet none take over. When the patterns show themselves, they are with different sounds. Like a cassette tape melted in the sun to create something entirely different.

Hailing from Sydney Australia, this is the first release by Melt Unit. We have a feeling his name will spread far and wide.

snippet.description:
Welcome to magic ingredient week! Every recipe I'll show you features a flavoring component that will turn any meal from ordinary to super delicious. Take today's magic ingredient: garlic oil. It couldn't be any easier to make: You simmer 1 head garlic in 1 cup olive oil, let sit, and  -- voila! --  a transformative flavor enhancer that dresses up everything from plain vegetables to marinades.

Sarah's Tip of the Day: 
Today I'll show you how to infuse the oil and use it to dress up some simple steamed vegetables (I'm using carrots and asparagus, but any combination will do). Tune in to the video to learn how to tell when the veggies are perfectly steamed. Plus, I'll show you one of my favorite kitchen prep tools. But the fun doesn't stop there: Come back tomorrow, and I'll use this magical oil to make a marinade for chicken. 

Subscribe for more easy and delicious recipes: http://full.sc/P8YgBt

---------------------------------------------------------------

Recipe Ingredients:
1 bunch asparagus (1 pound), ends trimmed
1 bunch carrots (1 pound), halved lengthwise
2 tablespoons Garlic Oil
Coarse salt and ground pepper

Get the full recipes:
http://www.marthastewart.com/852369/garlic-oil
http://www.marthastewart.com/852395/vegetables-garlic-oil

More Vegetarian Recipes: http://full.sc/P0o7Mt
---------------------------------------------------------------

Sarah Carey is the editor of Everyday Food magazine and her job is to come up with the best ways to make fast, delicious food at home. But she's also a mom to two hungry kids, so the question "What's for dinner?" is never far from her mind -- or theirs, it seems! Her days can get crazy busy (whose don't?), so these videos are all about her favorite fast, fresh meals -- and the tricks she uses to make it all SO much easier.

snippet.description:
Yuri Beliavsky, violin and Daniel Beliavsky, piano perform Cesar Franck's Violin-Piano Sonata in A, Mvt. III, at Christ & St. Stephen's Church, NYC, on September 18, 2005.  Reviewed by the Strad Magazine:  "Violinist Yuri Beliavsky shared a recital with his pianist son Daniel, who accompanied him in cultivated and mellifluous accounts of the Franck Sonata, Bruch's Kol Nidre and short works by Handel and Schubert."

Yuri Beliavsky was born in Moscow, USSR in 1932.  He studied violin with Professor Abraham Yampolsky and chamber music with the great Russian pianist Maria Yudina at the Gnesin State Music Institute in Moscow.  Beliavsky has been a member of the Grand Symphony Orchestra of Soviet Radio and Television, the Jerusalem Symphony Orchestra, and has taught at Jerusalem's Rubin Academy, and performed as soloist with both the Moscow Radio and the Israeli Radio.  Between 1972 and 1974, he made several recordings with the Jerusalem Symphony, among them Mozart's Concerto No.3 in G-Major, K. 216, Bartok's Violin Concerto No.1, and Bruch's Kol Nidre, which was recorded just before the Yom Kippur War, during which Yuri served in the Israeli Army.

Since 1975, Yuri has been with the Milwaukee Symphony Orchestra and has been on the
teaching faculty of the Music Institute of Chicago and the University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee, where he has often appeared in recitals with his son, pianist Daniel Beliavsky.  In 1983, Beliavsky recorded Lou Harrison's Concerto for Violin and Percussion Orchestra with the XX-Century Ensemble. 

In 1986-87, Beliavsky created a series of special programs for WFMR, the Classical Radio Station in Milwaukee, called "An Historical Perspective on the Art of Violin Playing since the Beginning of the Recording Era."  These 33 programs were broadcast during the 1986 and 1987 seasons during prime time and were very well received.  One of the highlights of these programs was the first international broadcast of a previously unknown Russian recording of ten year-old Jascha Heifetz made in 1911.

Yuri Beliavsky also gives lectures on the "Art of Violin Playing."  The most memorable of these lectures were given at the International Workshops in Austria and at the Gnesin Institute in Moscow, Russia.  These programs are broadcast on Davidzon Radio in New York City.

Yuri continues to perform actively in both Milwaukee and New York City.

snippet.description:
Find the recipe here http://karenmartini.com/cook/recipes/pavlova-roll-balsamic-basil-strawberry-raspberry-salad

Pavlova is a summer celebration in itself, sweet and decadent but with lots of seasonal fruit as well. I often find it too sweet so I came up with this version.  Instead of whipped cream, I use mascarpone and sheep's milk yoghurt, which gives this dessert a lovely sharpness.

Rolling your pavlova gives an impressive finish to the presentation and adds a lovely, unusual chewiness to the texture. It also makes it easier to transport if you're bringing a plate or having a picnic. Just pour over the berry salad and icing sugar when you arrive.

snippet.description:
You can watch it in 1080p. Races are natural 1080p, game videos and menus was 480p.
Musics are ingame sountracks.
Last two races of this epic game. 
I was listening the games music on Youtube then I decided play it again. And I can say that this game is the one of the most awesome game in arcade racing games! Even in 2012, game mechanics, musics, styles play itself. I finished it again in 5 days. That also reminded me old days those we were learning the modifying and tuning. It's too sad EA gave up on these kinds of games. Street racing and street cars had definitly different charms and auras. I am not against games like The Run, Hot Pursuit 2010 and Shift. But it would be great if EA sometimes make games like U, U2, MW, Carbon, UC. I know they already made 5 games, yet last one was 4 years ago and the Undercover was not a good game at all. At least it didn't satisfy me. So, since Carbon, it has been 6 years without modifying and tunning.
Now they are making new Most Wanted 2 but trailers show that it's not a game like first MW. Mostly a mix of Hot Pursuit and The Run. I hope the next game ends our thistiness of street races.

I used NFS Underground texture mod by Dragozool, you can see details here:
http://www.forum-3dcenter.org/vbulletin/showthread.php?t=491789
I also used Universal Widescreen Patcher to play in 1080p, you can find it here:
http://www.wsgf.org/software/universal-widescreen-uniws-patcher

I hope you enjoyed as much I enjoyed!

snippet.description:
How do you feel about the mounts in Warlords of Draenor? It seems as thought they've been given the short end of the development stick, with the only shiny and worthwhile mounts being in the cash store. I guess I'm not too happy that they don't have a method of acquisition in the game (i.e. not paying for it with $$) or even that the wow token isn't trade-able for anything on the store yet. That could be a really nice addition to the game and open up the store for everyone who doesn't want to spend a lot of real cash on a game they already pay to play!

One of the biggest complaints I see about the mounts introduced in Warlords is the variety. There's a lot of recolours and reskins, but not a great deal of new models. A great example of this is the new glory raiding mount - it's another wolf. It's a wolf model which has been in the game since WoD released as it's used quite often for fel touched wolves (and used even more in the new 6.2 patch).

It's a shame to see one of the most prestigious spots for mounts (a glory achievement!) have such a lackluster reward.

These are my thoughts on the current state of mounts in world of warcraft and why I think the game has gotten to where it is now.

snippet.description:
Piedi subito più belli! Via calli e duroni in un attimo e con la massima efficacia! Tutto questo grazie a Micro Pedi®, un accessorio semplicissimo da utilizzare, dotato di un rullo con superficie abrasiva da passare sopra l'area interessata.
Premendo il tasto, infatti, questo inizierà a girare (30 giri al secondo), andando così a levigare con energia: Micro Pedi® elimina così le callosità, riducendole letteralmente in polvere!
Con una comoda impugnatura ergonomica, è piccolo e leggero, perfetto da portare con sé anche in viaggio.
Da utilizzare esclusivamente sui piedi e sulla pelle asciutta.
Nella confezione, due rulli abrasivi.
Necessita di 2 batterie modello AA 1.5V (stilo), non incluse.
Dim. (L x H x P) 6 x 16 x 4 cm ca.

snippet.description:
My first multiplayer game in brawl buster's, i chose the boxer. 
Im not very good in this vid, still getting used to the game so be nice. =]

Brawl Busters is an online action combat that features innovative gameplay and a signature offbeat style like no other. Players can duke it out online using one of five incredibly unique classes: Boxer, Firefighter, Rocker, Slugger, and Blitzer. With a variety of single-player, multi-player, and co-op modes available, Brawl Busters has something for everyone.

Twisted cartoon world featuring high quality graphics and incredible animations.
Intuitive controls and seamless interface allows players to focus on the competition.
5 player classes with unique primary, secondary, and special attacks.
Fully customizable characters: Weapons, outfits, accessories, and more.
Interactive Environments: Destroy objects to earn power-ups, get high-ground advantage, teleport to new areas, and avoid environment hazards.
Combos: Chain attacks together to inflict extra damage and critical hits.

Eliot Patterson, co-founder of TRUE Skool, demonstrates the use of spray paint and paint markers on Crescent Graffiti Paper to create large scale graffiti pieces on the rolls and for sketching and developing work on the pads.

TRUE Skool's mission is to use cultural arts to educate and empower youth from different backgrounds and cultures to become leaders for positive social change in their communities. The constructive application and practice of Graffiti-style artwork is one thing they promote through demonstrations, classes and by creating murals in an effort to beautify communities.

snippet.description:
This generation has been brought up on toys, things that distract them from reality.  People are playing video games, continuously looking for new toys, things to occupy themselves with, forever unsatisfied and separated from reality. 
They escape reality with their toys. They are always looking for a new "kick" in life but they do not face reality. They never get to know Jesus Christ. Even Christians are playing around with studies, ipads and new gizmos instead of getting to know Jesus Christ. Relationships fall apart because people do not really talk to each other.  They text, senseless messages. They do not get to properly communicate and they do not get to know God, listen to God, be in His presence, be taught by Him, be led by Him. They are just looking for entertainment and escape.
Are you going after entertainment? Are you for ever looking for a new"kick," stimulation or are you looking for Jesus Christ. He will say to many believers in that day:"Go away I never knew you, you workers of wickedness." Because they were always PLAYING. They never got serious about Jesus Christ Himself but they were looking for stimulation, satisfaction and their own pleasure.
Are you seeking reality? Are you seeking Jesus Christ or do you occupy yourself with TOYS and are you PLAYING? Many people will miss eternity because they PLAYED THEIR LIFE AWAY. 
May Jesus bless you.


WITNESS FOR JESUS!
Visit me at: http://www.finalcall07.com
email: finalcall07@gmail.com

snippet.description:
Suicide Silence interview before 1st show with new line up at 2014 Soundwave Festival -- Ace Frehley + Peter Criss won't play in the KISS Rock & Roll Hall of Fame show -- The Acacia Strain vocalist shouts back at KORN's Jonathan Davis' political views - LOUDNESS have cancelled several North American shows - Comeback Kid have released a teaser of the track "Lower The Line"!

On Eddie Trunk Rocks from New York's Q104.3 FM, ex-KISS guitarist On Eddie Trunk Rocks be performing with KISS at the Rock And Roll Hall Of Fame induction. Trunk issued a recap of the conversation: "Ace Frehley called into my radio show live tonight and confirmed that he and Peter (Criss) are being denied the opportunity to perform at the R&R Hall Of Fame ceremony by Gene (Simmons) and Paul (Stanley), who will perform instead with the current band."

The Acacia Strain vocalist Vincent Bennett is questioning Korn's Jonathan Davis' political views such as that the US Government is using celebrities like Miley Cyrus as a smokescreen to help pass laws stripping away the rights of the U.S. citizens. Vincent recently tweeted:
"Yo Jonathan Davis; get a grip. This isn't the x-files. Insane political rants for attention. Ok. "I'm not a political person, but (insert 9 pages of internet fed beliefs, illuminati, lizard people, etc)."

Christina Rowatt of Soundwave TV had an interview with SUICIDE SILENCE today February 22 at the Brisbane show of the 2014 Soundwave festival in Australia. Interview  below.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=JGMmXu-2A1k

Comeback Kid have released a teaser of the track "Lower The Line" on their Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=10152288932223489&set=vb.24160438488&type=2&theater
Their  new album "Die Knowing" is out in March through Victory Records.

LOUDNESS have cancelled several North American shows, set in April. The band has recently stated:
"To our dear fans and supporters: 
We regret to inform you that we´ve had to cancel the previously announced US tour. The tour was scheduled by one of our US partners without our consent or knowledge. 
We were the last ones to learn about the tour itinerary only after they had already announced it publicly."

Sources: theprp, Bravewords, Blabbermouth

Plants vs. Zombies Garden Warfare digs into the trenches with an explosive new action experience. Blast zombies, plants and new characters across a mine-blowing world that delivers the depth of a traditional online shooter blended on high with the refreshing humor of Plant vs. Zombies. Take on Co-op and Multiplayer action with your friends and sow the seeds of victory!

Plants vs. Zombies Garden Warfare is a 3rd person shooter like no other, where players dig into the trenches to blast zombies and plants across a mine-blowing world that delivers depth blended with refreshing humor. You'll shoot peas from your face, invade the skies as a Garlic Drone and get to play as a zombie with a dolphin gun!

Powered by the advanced Frostbite 3 engine, Plants vs. Zombies Garden Warfare features stunning, three-dimensional worlds blooming with vibrant colors and unique landscapes. The game has more than 10 maps and three distinct modes: two 24-player 12 v 12 competitive multiplayer modes - Gardens & Graveyards and Team Vanquish - and Garden Ops, a four-player co-operative mode. You'll also find characters outfitted with special abilities, new gameplay mechanics and cool costumes.

MODES
GARDENS & GRAVEYARDS
In this massive 24-player mode, plants must defend their garden bases from zombie invasions - and you get to play either side! To capture a base, the zombies must conquer the garden and raise their tombstone - the more zombies that are in the garden area, the faster the tombstone rises. Once a base is captured, the combat shifts to the next garden objective.


TEAM VANQUISH
In the second mighty 24-player competitive mode, players square off directly and try to send the other team to the compost pile. Pick your side, powerful plant or fun-loving zombie, and let the botanical battle begin.


GARDEN OPS
This four-player co-operative mode is ideal for gamers that want to team up with their friends. The objective is simple - the Plant team must defeat waves and waves of zombies and zombie bosses like Gargantuar who are on the attack. Like in all modes, teamwork is crucial if you want your brains to survive.

snippet.description:
The KTM 1190 RC8 is a 1148 cc (70 cu in) v-twin sport bike manufactured by KTM.[1]. It is the Austrian manufacturer's first-ever Superbike design.
The first concept of the bike appeared in 2005, the concept bike was powered by the Super Duke 999 cc (60.9 cu in) v-twin, the bike capacity was increased to 1148 cc (70 cu in) for the production version. The bike features a steel trellis frame with a cast aluminium seat subframe. The suspension uses high-end upside-down forks and an alloy, double-sided swingarm manufactured by WP, a KTM subsidiary. The bike comes in two colours, the traditional KTM orange and a white and black version.
At the launch of the RC8 superbike KTM announced it will race in the RC8 in the FIM Superstock championship in 2008. KTM's two year plan is to get the bike regularly on the podium in superstock before moving up to the Superbike World Championship.

snippet.description:
Ensayo General celebrado el lunes 06/07/2015 de la "Antología de los Pabellones - Rincón del Veneno" dirigida por José Pérez Toledo "Pepe el Caja" y con la colaboración de José Gómez Díaz, propietario del Bar Los Pabellones, templo del Carnaval gaditano que se encontraba en la plaza de San Juan de Dios y que sigue vivo en el corazón de todos los que nos sentido en algún momento pabellonistas.

Cantan un pasodoble de la comparsa "Los Piratas" (1998) de Antonio Martínez Ares.

Con permiso, buenas tardes
vengo pa que me detenga
que cansá voy a sentarme
pues verá, voy a explicarle 
la historia de un sinvergüenza. 

Lo quería con locura
toa mi vía se la di
pero él solo buscaba
una criada, una esclava, 
una mujer para parir. 

Siempre decía
que tenía una quería, 
una duquesa para él,
Que le gustaba
llegar por la madrugada
pa tenerme a su merced. 

Y lo he matao,
a mi Juan yo lo he matao 
por haberme maltratao, 
por sentirme una perra, 
por hacerme una vieja 
con cuarenta y pocos años. 
Y lo he matao, a mi Juan yo lo he matao 
y en mi alcoba lo he dejao 
con mi llanto en sus labios. 

Justicia no pido yo, 
que conmigo no la habío
¿Quién me paga este dolor
y la pena de mis hijos?

Así que ya sabe usted,
haga lo que haya que hacer
póngame una soga al cuello, 
porque por primera vez...
no tengo, no tengo miedo.

Nuova Mercedes SL - Video Ufficiale
http://www.infomotori.com/video
Copyright Mercedes-Benz
==========
http://www.infomotori.com/auto/2010/01/14/mercedes-sl/
Nuova Mercedes Classe SL, le prime immagini ufficiali
La Nuova Mercedes Benz SL si prepara al debutto ufficiale nella nuova versione 2012, che va a sostituire il modello restyling del 2010. La cabrio di grandi dimensioni della casa automobilistica tedesca appare nella sua versione definitiva in queste prime immagini ufficiali rilasciate direttamente da Mercedes, dopo che alcune immagini catturate da una bozza del listino ufficiale circolante all'interno dell'azienda sono accidentalmente sfuggite al controllo degli adetti.

Nuovo design esterno simile ad SLK, CLS e Classe B
Possiamo così confermare le prime impressioni avute scrutando attraverso le camuffature del muletto visto nelle prime foto spia della Nuova Mercedes SL. Si notano immediatamente le linee morbide che caratterizzano il recente look del marchio della Stella, tanto che la nuova roadster assomiglia alla sorella più piccola, la compatta Nuova Mercedes SLK, oltre che a riprendere alcuni dettagli estetici da Mercedes CLS e Mercedes Classe B.

Design interno ripreso da Mercedes SLS AMG
La qualità degli interni, visibili in versione integrale nella nuova galleria di immagini e foto, è di assoluto livello, tanto da riprendere quella della versione sportiva top di gamma Mercedes SLS AMG, con volante a tre razze e strumentazione di tipo sportivo. Consolle compatta e plancia che si allunga verso il basso, occupando il posto solitamente destinato al cambio, sostituito da comandi posti dietro la corona del volante.

Motorizzazioni disponibili per Nuova Mercedes SL
Per quanto riguarda i motori saranno presenti le opzioni V6 e V8 benzina ad iniezione diretta, con potenza fino ai 557 cavalli della versione sportiva AMG. I consumi e le emissioni di CO2 verranno contenuti grazie alla riduzione del peso complessivo della vettura determinato dal largo uso dell'alluminio

snippet.description:
400GR DE BACALHAU DA NORUEGA DESFIADO
25OGR DE BATATAS
4 OVOS
1DL DE AZEITE
2 CEBOLAS
3 DENTES DE ALHO
1 MOLHO DE SALSA
SAL 
PIMENTA PRETA
E ÓLEO PARA FRITAR

1. Levamos um tacho com água e sal ao lume e colocamos as batatas a cozer.

2. Num outro tacho levamos água a ferver, juntamos o louro e os dentes de alho e colocamos o bacalhau a escaldar. Para os pastéis não é necessário usar as postas nobres. O rabo ou as abas servem muito bem.

3. Picamos as cebolas finamente, picamos também os dentes de alho e por último vamos picar a salsa.

4. Depois de escaldado o bacalhau vamos retirar a pele e as espinhas e vamos fazê-lo em lascas. Colocamos o bacalhau no centro de um pano, fechamos e vamos amassa-lo de modo a que o bacalhau faça fios.

5. As batatas já cozeram e vamos fazê-las em puré.

6. Levamos um tacho ao lume, juntamos um pouco de azeite e vamos refogar a cebola, juntamos a cebola e o dente de alho. Deixe que refogue até ficar bem loura e transparente, macia.

7. Juntamos o bacalhau, a batata e o refogado de cebola e a salsa. Juntamos agora as quatro gemas e vamos mexer muito bem. Batemos as claras em castelo e vamos envolver as claras na mistura. Com a ajuda de duas colheres vamos moldar bolinhos de bacalhau. 

8. Leve um tachinho ao lume, deixe aquecer bastante e vamos fritar os pastéis de bacalhau durante cerca de 2/3 minutos. Escorra-os em papel absorvente.  

A MAIS MUNDIALMENTE FAMOSA RECEITA DE BACALHAU DA NORUEGA
